    • Uses of IContainerItemAccessor in de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor

      Classes in de.axnsoftware.settings.impl.accessor that implement IContainerItemAccessor 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl
      The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all Array properties.
      class  AbstractContainerItemAccessorImpl<T>
      The abstract class AbstractArrayItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived classes and provides default behaviour for all implementations of the IAccessor interface.
      class  AbstractListItemAccessorImpl
      The abstract class AbstractListItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all List like properties.
      class  AbstractMapItemAccessorImpl
      The abstract class AbstractMapItemAccessorImpl models the root of a hierarchy of derived implementation classes and it provides the default behaviour for all implementations of the IContainerItemAccessor interface for all Map like properties.
      class  BranchArrayItemAccessorImpl
      The final class BranchArrayItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing items in ArrayS that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
      class  BranchListItemAccessorImpl
      The final class BranchListItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing items in ListS that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
      class  BranchMapItemAccessorImpl
      The final class BranchMapItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing items in MapS that are instances of PropertyClass annotated classes.
      class  LeafArrayItemAccessorImpl
      The final class LeafArrayItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of ArrayS, such as Integer or EnumS.
      class  LeafListItemAccessorImpl
      The final class LeafListItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of ListS, such as Integer or EnumS.
      class  LeafMapItemAccessorImpl
      The final class LeafMapItemAccessorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IAccessor interface, responsible for accessing simple type items of MapS, such as Integer or EnumS.
